dos iz gevezn bay LYON?

00:11:21.475 --> 00:11:22.903
dos iz gevezn.

00:11:22.943 --> 00:11:25.398
an andere, dos iz gevezn LYON

00:11:25.398 --> 00:11:27.688
ober lomir zogn az s'iz azoy vi

00:11:27.688 --> 00:11:29.868
HERTZLIYA fun TEL AVIV.

00:11:29.868 --> 00:11:33.467
azoy iz es gevezn, a bisele in droysn.

00:11:34.553 --> 00:11:35.576
un

00:11:35.582 --> 00:11:39.991
m'hot gevoynt oyf di finefte shtok. dos iz nisht gevezn keyn problem

00:11:39.991 --> 00:11:43.617
un di mame hot gezogt, un mayn bruder iz geganen arbetn.

00:11:43.617 --> 00:11:46.317
er hot shoyn gebrengt oykhet gelt in shtub

00:11:46.399 --> 00:11:48.117
un zi hot gezogt

00:11:48.117 --> 00:11:52.454
"me ken nisht blaybn di gantse mishpokhe tsuzamen, vayl tomer s'vet epes pasirn"

00:11:52.454 --> 00:11:55.854
koydem kol di kinder. dos iz gevezn ir gantse lebn.

00:11:55.854 --> 00:11:58.534
nor di kinder, azoy vi a yidishe mame.

00:11:58.887 --> 00:12:01.870
un zi hot, zi hot

00:12:01.870 --> 00:12:03.212
m'hot

00:12:03.212 --> 00:12:07.464
m'iz gevezn in kontakt, ikh veys nisht mit, vi azoy, mit OZER.

00:12:07.464 --> 00:12:10.890
dos iz gevezn an organizatsye vos hot zikh

00:12:10.890 --> 00:12:13.410
vos hot geholfn di yidishe kinder.

00:12:14.277 --> 00:12:17.882
un zi hot gezogt "me ken aroysshikn di kinder."

00:12:18.158 --> 00:12:18.897
un

00:12:18.897 --> 00:12:20.666
m'hot undz aroysgeshikt

00:12:20.858 --> 00:12:25.369
vayter in droysn fun yen- efsher draysik kilometer.

00:12:25.369 --> 00:12:27.011
fun d- fun dort.

00:12:27.304 --> 00:12:30.909
un m'iz dort ongekumen in a mishpokhe.

00:12:31.422 --> 00:12:34.355
s'iz gevezn azoy oyf a hoykhe barg

00:12:34.355 --> 00:12:37.654
un s'iz gevezn zeyer frume mentshn iberal

00:12:37.654 --> 00:12:40.554
vayl iberal iz gevezn di groyse

00:12:40.554 --> 00:12:42.834
Yoshke azoy oyf a sh-

00:12:42.834 --> 00:12:45.370
oyf a UNK azoy

00:12:45.370 --> 00:12:48.730
un yeder eyner vos iz adurkhgeganen hot zikh geKREUTZt

00:12:48.757 --> 00:12:51.581
un dos un yents, ober undz hot men gornisht gemakht.

00:12:52.060 --> 00:12:56.208
iz hot men prubirt nisht tsu geyn mit di CHAVEROT ven me kumt tsurik

00:12:56.208 --> 00:12:58.710
vayl ale mol m'hot undz gezogt, hot men gezogt

00:12:58.710 --> 00:13:00.120
"undz ze'mir ATHEE."

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:02.296
ATHEE dos heyst nisht keyn gloybn.

00:13:02.522 --> 00:13:03.967
dos iz es.

00:13:05.155 --> 00:13:05.970
ober

00:13:05.970 --> 00:13:08.709
m'hot zikh nisht gefilt azoy bakvem

00:13:08.783 --> 00:13:13.924
un m'iz geblibn bay di froy. m'hot nisht gegat keyn rekht tsu shraybn in shtub.

00:13:14.098 --> 00:13:16.927
m'hot nisht gegat keyn shum kontakt

00:13:17.727 --> 00:13:21.107
un dos iz gevezn zeyer shver. ober vos?

00:13:21.107 --> 00:13:22.884
m'iz gevezn tsvey

00:13:22.941 --> 00:13:24.639
mit mayn shvester.

00:13:25.050 --> 00:13:26.900
di MADAME hot geheysn

00:13:26.900 --> 00:13:28.440
MADAME DE PIETRIE.

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:30.340
zey hobn nisht gegat keyn kinder.

00:13:30.340 --> 00:13:32.780
zey hobn gevoynt in aza kleyne hayzke

00:13:32.780 --> 00:13:34.520
mit a GINA MESAVIV

00:13:34.520 --> 00:13:36.924
un dort iz men gevezn.

00:13:37.926 --> 00:13:41.075
un s'iz nisht gevezn tsu esn

00:13:41.368 --> 00:13:44.771
iz di broyt vos zi hot geshnitn

00:13:44.929 --> 00:13:47.589
zi hot es geshnit azoy din

00:13:47.713 --> 00:13:51.296
az ven zi hot geleygt a bisele RIBA fun oybn

00:13:51.296 --> 00:13:53.608
iz es aropgekrokhn fun untn

00:13:53.608 --> 00:13:55.554
vayl s'hot zikh nisht gehaltn.

00:13:55.695 --> 00:13:59.860
iz vos hot men gegat fun tsvey dine, kleyne

00:13:59.860 --> 00:14:03.049
dos in di fri mit epes tsu trinken.

00:14:03.049 --> 00:14:04.804
m'iz ge- arumgeganen

00:14:04.804 --> 00:14:06.556
BEETSEM hungerik.

00:14:06.816 --> 00:14:08.972
un m'hot zi gezogt "me ken nisht

00:14:08.972 --> 00:14:12.339
hobn a, nokh a UNK?" "ah" zogt zi, "s'iz nisht meglekh.

00:14:12.339 --> 00:14:15.609
mayn man arbet in, in va- a vayn gesheft.

00:14:15.609 --> 00:14:18.259
er toysht vayn oyf broyt."

00:14:18.882 --> 00:14:21.053
iz, dos iz ales.

00:14:22.189 --> 00:14:24.818
un m'hot nisht gevust vi azoy

00:14:24.818 --> 00:14:25.980
me ken

00:14:26.442 --> 00:14:29.420
araynkumen. mayn shvester iz gevezn di gantse

00:14:29.420 --> 00:14:31.930
kop fun dem. zi hot gezogt "du zog nisht

00:14:31.930 --> 00:14:35.040
un UNK zog nisht." zi hot mir gegebn a knip fun hintn

00:14:35.040 --> 00:14:36.720
ven ikh hob epes gevolt.

00:14:36.752 --> 00:14:38.841
kh'hob gegat moyre fun ir

00:14:38.841 --> 00:14:41.151
ober zi hot gegat aza

00:14:41.153 --> 00:14:44.469
oytomatishe farshtand

00:14:44.469 --> 00:14:46.061
vos un ven.

00:14:46.472 --> 00:14:48.090
un zi hot zikh gemakht

00:14:48.090 --> 00:14:50.310
zeyer gut

00:14:50.310 --> 00:14:52.790
mit ⟨eyne⟩ CHAVERA un mit di mishpokhe.

00:14:52.790 --> 00:14:55.562
zi iz dokh arayngeganen mit alemen

00:14:55.635 --> 00:14:58.146
un eyn mol hot zi zikh tseveynt.

00:14:58.146 --> 00:15:00.455
zi hot gebroykht tsu hobn a BUL

00:15:00.647 --> 00:15:03.239
oyf tsu kenen shraybn far di eltern.

00:15:04.427 --> 00:15:05.480
iz

00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:09.280
u- un ikh, di ershte mol vos ikh ze mayn shvester vos zi veynt

00:15:09.280 --> 00:15:11.640
vayl zi iz a shtarke. zi veynt nisht.

00:15:11.640 --> 00:15:13.199
hob ikh mitgeveynt.

00:15:13.199 --> 00:15:16.048
hot es gemakht a, a groyse ROSHEM

00:15:16.257 --> 00:15:17.215
un

00:15:17.215 --> 00:15:20.475
di froy hot genumen, zi hot gezogt "OKAY

00:15:20.475 --> 00:15:23.485
do hostu far a BUL

00:15:23.648 --> 00:15:25.093
tsu kenen shikn."

00:15:25.437 --> 00:15:28.520
un dort in di gegnt iz gevezn aza plats

00:15:28.520 --> 00:15:32.150
vu di yugnt iz gekumen oyf tsu makhn SKATING.

00:15:32.372 --> 00:15:36.500
s'iz nisht gevezn genoy azoy vi haynt, ober mit fir redlekh

00:15:36.507 --> 00:15:40.077
un s'iz gekumen fun LYON, fun di hoypt shtot oykhet

00:15:40.077 --> 00:15:42.257
s'iz gevezn a bakante plats.

00:15:42.531 --> 00:15:45.799
hot men gemakht aza TOCHNIT

00:15:45.889 --> 00:15:48.617
az mayn bruder, ale mol der zelber

00:15:48.623 --> 00:15:52.481
er geyt dort kumen. m'hot im gegebn genoy di adres

00:15:52.504 --> 00:15:54.830
un m'vet zogn far di mishpokhe

00:15:54.830 --> 00:15:57.620
az m'hot im dort getrofn mit CHAVERIM.

00:15:57.620 --> 00:15:59.799
er iz gekumen makhn SKATING

00:15:59.799 --> 00:16:02.680
in dem plats, vayl undz hot men nisht gegat vos.

00:16:02.680 --> 00:16:04.330
m'hot ale mol gekukt dort

00:16:04.381 --> 00:16:06.770
vi mentshn dreyen zikh arop, aroyf.

00:16:06.770 --> 00:16:08.680
s'iz gevezn an atraktsye.

00:16:09.750 --> 00:16:13.645
azoy iz es gevezn, un ven m'hot derzen di bruder

00:16:13.645 --> 00:16:15.414
dos iz gevezn

00:16:15.437 --> 00:16:18.671
a freyd vos me ken zikh nisht forshteln.

00:16:18.913 --> 00:16:20.606
un m'hot im gebrengt

00:16:20.606 --> 00:16:23.854
in shtub dort, un m'hot im gezogt "kuk

00:16:23.854 --> 00:16:26.200
ver m'hot getrofn PITOM."

00:16:26.200 --> 00:16:29.634
er iz gekumen sh- mit zayne CHAVERIM, mit dos un ye-

00:16:29.634 --> 00:16:31.590
"ah dos iz di bruder? oh

00:16:31.590 --> 00:16:34.320
ober du megst nisht hobn keyn kontakt." s'iz

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:37.940
geshribn dos, un m'hot im, un, ober s'iz

00:16:37.940 --> 00:16:42.810
BEMIKRE a tsufal, ahin aher, un m'iz im geganen tsurikfirn

00:16:42.810 --> 00:16:46.170
un m'hot im gezogt "undz muz men fun do aroysgeyn

00:16:46.170 --> 00:16:48.374
vayl di mentsh, er iz nisht keyn

00:16:48.374 --> 00:16:50.610
normale mentsh, un er hot

00:16:50.610 --> 00:16:52.400
gezukht, un dos ye-"

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:54.510
mayn shvester hot glaykh gefilt

00:16:54.510 --> 00:16:57.062
az s'iz, epes iz nisht BESEDER.

00:16:57.928 --> 00:16:59.474
er hot dos gehert

00:16:59.717 --> 00:17:02.169
un m'iz undz gekumen

00:17:02.169 --> 00:17:03.390
take zukhn.

00:17:03.413 --> 00:17:06.124
fun di, oykhet fun di organizatsye.

00:17:07.277 --> 00:17:09.130
un m'hot undz gebrengt

00:17:09.130 --> 00:17:10.733
tsurik in shtub arayn

00:17:10.733 --> 00:17:13.779
un s'iz gekumen, s'iz gevezn zumer tsayt.

00:17:13.779 --> 00:17:15.739
zumer tsayt hot men gezogt "ah

00:17:15.739 --> 00:17:17.849
di kinder, me ken zey nokh a mol shikn

00:17:17.879 --> 00:17:20.039
oyf zumer vakatsye."

00:17:20.423 --> 00:17:21.395
gut.

00:17:21.587 --> 00:17:26.542
iz men nokh a mol geforn. s'iz gevezn mit a tsug vos hot geheysn LE TRAIN BLEU.

00:17:26.548 --> 00:17:28.806
s'iz geganen in a gevise plats

00:17:28.806 --> 00:17:30.804
un nokh a mol in a shule

00:17:30.804 --> 00:17:32.614
in di CHATSER fun di shule

00:17:32.614 --> 00:17:33.844
ale kinder

00:17:33.844 --> 00:17:36.264
azoy vi beheymes ken men zogn

00:17:36.264 --> 00:17:38.024
zenen gevezn azoy

00:17:38.024 --> 00:17:39.384
tsuzamen

00:17:39.384 --> 00:17:42.250
un di mentshn vos zey hobn gevolt oyfnemen kinder

00:17:42.250 --> 00:17:44.430
zenen zikh gekumen kloybn

00:17:44.605 --> 00:17:45.831
poshet.

00:17:45.921 --> 00:17:48.420
hot men gezogt "s'iz do a groyse

00:17:48.420 --> 00:17:50.340
CHATEAU, a groyse plats

00:17:50.340 --> 00:17:51.720
vos zey nemen

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:53.510
draysik kinder oyf eyn mol."

00:17:53.510 --> 00:17:55.970
un ikh zog far mayn shvester "oh, a CHATEAU?

00:17:55.970 --> 00:17:57.250
dos ken zayn"

00:17:57.250 --> 00:18:00.680
"neyn" zogt zi. "dort vu s'iz do a sakh kinder vet gornisht vert zayn.

00:18:00.680 --> 00:18:02.010
undz darf men hobn"

00:18:02.010 --> 00:18:04.708
yede zakh, zi hot gegat aza khush

00:18:04.708 --> 00:18:06.063
keyneynehore

00:18:06.222 --> 00:18:07.144
un

00:18:07.386 --> 00:18:10.251
OKAY, un zi kloybt zikh oys

00:18:10.251 --> 00:18:12.478
a mentsh vos zi hot dort gezen.

00:18:12.478 --> 00:18:14.268
a elegante froy

00:18:14.268 --> 00:18:16.326
sheyn geputst mit ales.

00:18:16.326 --> 00:18:18.663
zi zogt "zi gefelt mir."

00:18:18.663 --> 00:18:20.992
nisht di andere hot undz gekloybn

00:18:20.992 --> 00:18:23.186
ober zi hot zi geklibn

00:18:23.186 --> 00:18:27.316
un zi hot gezogt "zi zet oys azoy eydele mit alemen.

00:18:27.316 --> 00:18:29.430
ven zi dreyt zikh

00:18:29.430 --> 00:18:31.936
undz zol men zayn far ire oygn."

00:18:31.936 --> 00:18:33.952
un azoy hot zi mir geshlept

00:18:33.952 --> 00:18:36.362
fun eyn zayt in di andere zayt

00:18:36.362 --> 00:18:38.762
un zi hot zikh umgekukt "UNK"

00:18:38.762 --> 00:18:40.692
un nokh a mol m'iz far di oygn

00:18:40.692 --> 00:18:42.772
un nokh a mol gekukt, nokh a mol

00:18:42.772 --> 00:18:46.144
biz zi hot gezogt "ah, do ikh ze tsvey meydelekh

00:18:46.144 --> 00:18:50.390
zenen zey azoy zis mit ales. vi azoy heystu?"

00:18:50.390 --> 00:18:52.290
un me heybt on tsu zogn un dos

00:18:52.290 --> 00:18:55.220
un zi zogt "ober ikh ken nor nemen," undz zogt men

00:18:55.220 --> 00:18:56.820
undz ze'mir tsvey shvester

00:18:56.820 --> 00:18:59.349
 m'iz tsugevoynt tsu zayn tsuzamen

00:18:59.349 --> 00:19:00.973
ober zi zogt "neyn. ikh

00:19:00.973 --> 00:19:02.433
ken nor nemen eyns

00:19:02.433 --> 00:19:04.743
ober ikh hob a shokhnte vos zi hot mir gezogt

00:19:04.743 --> 00:19:07.202
az zi iz greyt tsu nemen an andere."

00:19:07.596 --> 00:19:11.300
un mayn shvester hot bashlosn "OKAY, du vest geyn bay ir

00:19:11.300 --> 00:19:13.920
un ikh vel geyn bay di sh- vayl du bist klener

00:19:13.920 --> 00:19:15.930
vest dikh nisht kenen gebn an eytse.

00:19:15.930 --> 00:19:17.830
ikh vel mir yo gebn an eytse."

00:19:17.830 --> 00:19:19.490
azoy iz es gevezn.

00:19:19.490 --> 00:19:22.907
un do iz es gevezn a herlekhe moment

00:19:22.907 --> 00:19:25.700
vayl di froy, zey hobn nisht gegat keyn kinder

00:19:25.700 --> 00:19:28.320
a porfolk, efsher hot zi gegat draysik yor.

00:19:28.320 --> 00:19:30.832
zi hot mir oysgezen zeyer alt damolst

00:19:30.832 --> 00:19:32.044
mit alemen.

00:19:32.044 --> 00:19:34.572
ober s'iz gevezn a OZERET

00:19:34.765 --> 00:19:37.760
vos zi hot azoy sheyn geklapt oyfn gloz

00:19:37.760 --> 00:19:40.220
"JOSIE, LA SUITE S'IL VOUS PLAIT."

00:19:40.220 --> 00:19:41.740
azoy hot zi gezogt

00:19:41.740 --> 00:19:43.520
"breng di nekste zakh"

00:19:43.520 --> 00:19:46.500
un azoy vayter. un m'hot mir gelokt di hor

00:19:46.500 --> 00:19:50.160
un m'hot mir genumen RUBAN in di kop

00:19:50.160 --> 00:19:53.110
un m'hot mir gekoyft, zakhn

00:19:53.226 --> 00:19:56.443
un m'hot mir oysgelernt sheyn tsu redn

00:19:56.550 --> 00:20:00.830
vayl er hot mir ale mol genumen, un er hot mir gezogt

00:20:00.938 --> 00:20:02.453
"nisht azoy zogt men

00:20:02.453 --> 00:20:03.643
un do hostu

00:20:03.643 --> 00:20:04.810
tashn gelt

00:20:04.810 --> 00:20:05.740
un tomer

00:20:05.740 --> 00:20:08.740
d'vest makhn a grayz muzstu mir tsurikgebn."

00:20:08.835 --> 00:20:13.400
iz, hob ikh ale mol gut oyfgepast, un ven s'iz gekumen mentshn hot men zikh

00:20:13.400 --> 00:20:15.580
sheyn azoy gebroykht tsu ⟨betn⟩

00:20:15.580 --> 00:20:16.980
iz dos, un

00:20:16.980 --> 00:20:19.000
bay sof azoy gezogt "ikh vil

00:20:19.000 --> 00:20:20.660
dikh adoptirn.

00:20:22.420 --> 00:20:24.489
ikh vil redn mit dayne eltern."

00:20:24.563 --> 00:20:25.856
un

00:20:26.149 --> 00:20:28.725
mayn mame iz shnel gekumen

00:20:28.917 --> 00:20:34.477
mitn kleyne oyf di hent, un zi hot gezogt "ikh ⟨dankbar⟩ zeyer

00:20:34.477 --> 00:20:38.087
oyf alemen vos hobn gemakht bay undz mit alemen

00:20:38.181 --> 00:20:40.987
ober keyn kind git men nisht avek."

00:20:40.987 --> 00:20:44.778
dos iz, dos kumt nisht in di sh- in di frage.

00:20:44.778 --> 00:20:46.508
ah, hobn zey gezogt OKAY.

00:20:46.508 --> 00:20:49.666
un dort iz geshen di LIBERATION

00:20:49.909 --> 00:20:53.143
in dem moment. dos iz gevezn in oygust

00:20:53.571 --> 00:20:55.151
fir un fertsik

00:20:55.309 --> 00:20:56.315
BEETSEM.

00:20:56.355 --> 00:20:58.222
dos iz damolst gevezn

00:20:58.245 --> 00:21:02.477
un m'hot gezen fun di groyse mapes UNK vos s'iz gevezn dort

00:21:02.477 --> 00:21:04.177
ale daytshn

00:21:04.177 --> 00:21:06.727
geyen avek mit a, oyf nayem

00:21:06.727 --> 00:21:08.787
mit a ⟨halte⟩ dos, un mit

00:21:08.787 --> 00:21:12.229
ales flit avek mit di kop arop.

00:21:12.572 --> 00:21:16.450
un dos iz gevezn a oysname HARGASHA

00:21:16.450 --> 00:21:18.846
vos m'hot gezen az

00:21:18.846 --> 00:21:23.298
zey, zey geyen avek, un zey antloyfn BEETSEM.

00:21:23.727 --> 00:21:27.821
un undz ze'mir dort nokh a bisele geblibn

00:21:28.249 --> 00:21:30.909
un m'iz tsurikgekumen in di heym

00:21:31.675 --> 00:21:35.844
un m'hot gevart biz s'hot zikh mamesh ales

00:21:35.844 --> 00:21:37.574
geendikt. m'hot gezen di

00:21:37.574 --> 00:21:39.944
PRISONNIERS, di ayngefangene sht-

00:21:39.944 --> 00:21:42.488
di mentshn vos zey hobn ongehoybn, hot zey gemakht

00:21:42.488 --> 00:21:46.488
arbetn mit ales. m'hot afilek nisht gekukt oyf zey. m'hot gezogt

00:21:46.488 --> 00:21:50.113
"gants gut." di nekome iz gevezn azoy groys.

00:21:50.271 --> 00:21:53.167
un m'iz tsurikgeforn keyn Pariz.

00:21:53.899 --> 00:21:56.036
m'iz tsurikgeforn keyn Pariz.

00:21:56.346 --> 00:22:00.021
damolst hot men gornisht getrofn. ales hot men gegat

00:22:00.021 --> 00:22:01.081
erleydikt

00:22:01.392 --> 00:22:02.820
fun di shtub.

00:22:03.265 --> 00:22:08.318
s'iz gornisht gevezn. hot men ongehoybn tsurik, ikh veys nisht vi azoy

00:22:08.318 --> 00:22:11.338
vos un ven, ober do a bet un do a tish

00:22:11.338 --> 00:22:13.124
un do ahin un aher

00:22:13.124 --> 00:22:15.816
